Package badlib

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Path
    This class takes in specific inputs for how the robot should be moving over a period of time and creates a path from that information.
    PathData
    Takes periods of acceleration for angle and position and puts this data into a form usable by PathMath (thru Path).
    PathMath
    This is a helper class for the Path class.
    Period
    A period of time during which some amount is changing (or not if Period.rate is zero).
    Point
    An extremely simple class, pretty much a struct.
